description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone to join our busy and friendly Pathology Specimen Reception team at the Conquest Hospital. Our reception team are responsible for booking all pathology samples onto the laboratory computer system and ensuring correct protocols are followed for the handling and movement of those samples. Accuracy of work is very important.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a part-time post. 25 hours / week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will involve some specimen preparation ready for analysing. There will be a requirement to work some weekends as part of a rotation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Familiarity with clinical terminology is advantageous but not essential. Training will be given.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lesley White Specimen Reception Supervisor Email address Lesley.white6@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
